   Output: document
   Sample Size: 5
   Sample Reservoir Method: Materialize
   ->  Index Scan using wildcard_all on documentdb_data.documents_25712007 collection
         Output: document
         Index Cond: (collection.document @> '{ "value" : { "$numberInt" : "100" } }'::bson)
