----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 Custom Scan (DocumentDBApiReservoirSample)
   Output: document
   Sample Size: 5
   Sample Reservoir Method: Heap Skip
   ->  Index Scan using a_1 on documentdb_data.documents_25712014 collection
         Output: document
         Index Cond: (collection.document @>= '{ "a" : { "$numberInt" : "0" } }'::bson)
(7 rows)

